# Flockctl — Environment Variables
#
# Flockctl is local-first and runs as a single Node process with SQLite (WAL).
# No Postgres, Redis, JWT, or Docker. The daemon binds to 127.0.0.1 by default.
# API keys (Anthropic / OpenAI / Gemini) are stored in the SQLite database via
# the UI or CLI — do NOT put them here.
#
# Copy to .env only if you need to override a default.

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────
#  Backend
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────

# Override the Flockctl home directory (contains SQLite db, logs, config).
# Default: ~/.flockctl
# FLOCKCTL_HOME=/custom/path/.flockctl

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────
#  Frontend (build-time, Vite)
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────

# Base URL the UI uses to reach the daemon. Leave empty for same-origin.
# Only set this if you serve the UI from a different host than the daemon.
# VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:52077

# Dev-proxy target for `vite dev` (ui/vite.config.ts). Only needed if the
# daemon runs on a non-default port during development.
# VITE_API_TARGET=http://localhost:52077

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────
#  Live tests (optional — tests/live/*)
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────

# FLOCKCTL_LIVE_TESTS=1
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...
